            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "a39313bd-44d6-4697-94c0-8ddc9e9dbf95",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "amount": "3",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "9e76af6b-ca07-4986-a583-f18306d3e4fa",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "All right, everyone, today we're going to combine our steam-powered engine with the magic rune for 'energy\" onto a sturdy oak handle with a triggering device.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "61743fa4-3f3c-48dd-9e4a-0eac5de76b20",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "When we have this baby finished, you'll have your very own Zap Gun!",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "ca0f170f-c67f-48fe-b295-f048f6500ea9",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Now, a word of warning before we begin... this is a very dangerous device. You will be holding incredible power in your hand. Whatever you do, don't point the weapon at yourself or another person. ",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "39339b50-70b3-46c0-8a5f-479b4f35952d",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "You don't want to tempt an itchy trigger finger, no matter how annoying that person may be.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "9c8297bb-d763-496b-a8a7-cb2a0a09cca6",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "This Zap Gun can discharge up to five or six charges of energy bolts per day. Then it will have to build up enough static energy to recharge over night. While it does not affect non-corporal Undead, it will be quite useful against the physical metaphysical beings.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "395d9866-c97a-47f4-9fcf-c1f83ebd7648",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Oh, and another thing, tomorrow is the final exam for this class. I expect you will all do as well as you did last time.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeInventory",
                    "id": "d791f1a3-dbab-4bda-a86b-a4944e10ccc2",
                    "propId": "9451cdac-c4b4-46dc-98e8-7c0f10eb03ed",
                    "sceneId": "a2508b7e-a177-4a96-93bd-4d8ab88dffc4",
                    "change": "1",
                    "count": 1,
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "d87ef81a-fb18-4656-a961-e4b2f0115d41",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "There's a lot of accomplish and only a limited time to do it, so gentlebeings, get your guns!",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.addJournalEntry",
                    "id": "18d84d01-468f-4784-8831-9f80258a3d12",
                    "name": "Zap to it!",
                    "notify": true,
                    "description": "We made the Zap Gun today. Can't wait to see what it does."
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
